QuestData.Title: What We Know of the Naga
QuestData.Description:
It feels good to be me again. I have you to thank for that.
My head still hurts from the zoatroid's influence, but I think the others are worse off.
Put some of this salve on their wounds, and I'll do my best to tell you what I know about the naga.
QuestData.LogDescription: Tend to the Kelfin's wounds and hear what Fenn has to say about the naga.
